         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">22/8/66 ¶ My dear Sir Redmond, ¶  ¶ Is it too late to write to the British Consul in the Fiji Islands for contributions to our Exhibition? I think not, as the communication from Sydney is frequent and...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">66.08.22a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Redmond Barry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 4, VPRS 927/P0000<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Correspondence relating to various exhibitions, Trustees of the Public Library, Museums and National Gallery of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">22/8/66</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir Redmond,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Is it too late to write to the British Consul in the Fiji Islands for contributions to our Exhibition? I think not, as the communication from Sydney is frequent and rapid, nor would it be necessary that these articles should be here at the very commencement of the Exhibition. The Fiji and indeed others of the Pacific Islands are commercially closely related to Australia, and their products of wool, cotton, cocosoil,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>coconut oil?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>spices, sago, arrow-root &amp;c are important. In the Fiji now large<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Mocca Coffee</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M sent<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>three<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>plants to Fiji c.1862, describing them as 'mocha coffee' (M to J. McCulloch, 30 September 1865; B65.O8.07; B65.10.02).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>In<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>B95.08.04,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>p. 134, he identifies<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'Mocha-coffee'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as a variety of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Coffea arabica</seg>.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>plantations exist from<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">one</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>original plant I sent there from this Garden<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS inscription probably by Barry: 'Copy of Letter to Gov of N Caledonia &amp; the [...] for Consul of Fiji Islands'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
         </div>
